{
  "texts": [
    "Artificial neural networks are now being used or tested in many different fields.",
    "These include, for example, natural language processing and speech or image recognition.",
    "Common business applications include quality management, pro-duction or sales planning, maintenance processes and credit rating systems.",
    "ANNs also play a role in research and development, e.g.",
    "in autonomous driving or biotechnology."
  ]
}